Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第十一回  「金崎的退路」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個不剩  都給我砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.67,0:02:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良大人  由我們來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七  帶著兄弟快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田家的猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有墨俁一夜城的話  我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈和猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死都不會放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領  快逃  趁現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能扔下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半七！半七！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…大…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.57,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你投靠織田真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把槍就賞你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良  良晴先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  你要平安回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出來多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾張兵還有一部分在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正情況簡直亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  去救他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去只是找死而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是憑自己的意志留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護頭領你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真柄姐妹立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍的殿後部隊完全崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的花只會在戰場綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想讓織田的公主們在余懷抱之中綻放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈已經撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有相良良晴率領的五百人左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田的猴子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長政對他的評價很不錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍突入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良良晴的人頭  一定是我們淺井家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光秀小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠猴子前輩  想活下來是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去救良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能光顧自己逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良良晴在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被淺井搶先了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵將的首級由我等來取！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.71,0:06:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六郎太！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的目標是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上拿大將的人頭才是目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要說是墨俁一夜城的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人頭的價值肯定是很高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有那種價值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懸賞嗎？不如我們來殺了相良也是一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫這個男人逃脫已經是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在這裡  和夥伴們一起戰死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的屍體聽到這話一定很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己捨命保護的男人  居然要選擇屈死於此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈  應該也是想說和你一樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  她選擇了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈是這個國家  大家都必需的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想讓我怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說就是命的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了夥伴  你能去死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我絕對不會捨棄夥伴逃走的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是貪心  不拿到所有的東西是不會滿足的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就死在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田家的猴子  滾出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡開始就四散而逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被老大吩咐保護你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果聚在一起的話  會全滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死啊  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人回來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡看到的  不要說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標只有我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能放過其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的請求  是武士的情義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都是你不配用的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了  假面大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些士兵就由我來給義景說情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安心去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敵人拿走首級  是恥辱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  相良良晴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前  前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光秀小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良…前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是保住了性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.85,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算脫去了鎧甲  還是把這個貼身留著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此擋住了子彈  削弱了威力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他…他死了都在保護公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人她…公主大人她拋棄了哥哥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊  猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是夢囈而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在呼喚著猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊  猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐快死了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被狙擊了  不知道能不能撐過明天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去  有人嗎  放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該即死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:59.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈難道有上天保佑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跟死了沒什麼兩樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不通…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人已經沒用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  那傢伙的任務已經完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過金崎的朝倉·淺井聯合軍三萬五千人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始往京城進軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柴田勝家率領的織田軍  以一萬五千兵力對陣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.12,0:12:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比叡山附近  坂本附近對峙著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破的話京城就會陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總大將·信奈不在的織田軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可以說是陷入絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴大人  粉身碎骨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼服部半藏要把良晴大人給…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把半藏叫來  問個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在他已經保護著元康大人  返回三河了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田軍可是大敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個  現在問題在於公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她知道了相良良晴死了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒法活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說彈正大人對醫術也頗有研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能救救公主大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心病是醫術所無法治療的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.32,0:13:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的辦法  只有強制療法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓信奈大人自己去接受相良良晴的死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許不會再醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝能誓下終生之愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子  你沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  婚禮的時候不要說夢話好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝願認同相良良晴為夫  起誓終生不渝之愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意起誓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是夢的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請進行誓約之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能從你這裡拿到恩賞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我可是天下第一的美少女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你等到現在  真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信您會醒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺腦子一片空白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用了秘藥  把夢和現實連接了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人  傷還沒好  不能起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他…死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被炸彈粉身碎骨  聽說連屍體都沒留下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  公主大人  我沒能救下良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  已經見不到他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明智光秀也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵衛也？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是高貴的犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他們  信奈大人也一定要完成天下統一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下統一…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙我們的敵人仍然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪走了信奈大人的重要的人的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您打算就這樣放過他們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能原諒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  必須去復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子他們的  仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思  彈正大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈大人她需要活下去的糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來代替相良良晴的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憤怒是最大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下一定會是信奈大人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代  趕緊去軍師大人那一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不祥的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田軍把天王寺給燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是公主大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個堺可是有任何大名都不能進攻的規矩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人到底怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋了  沒有信奈的織田軍只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織  織田信奈！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為猴子和十兵衛的復仇之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全部殺光！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會錯  那就是織田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公  快迎擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒勝算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃回近江吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣就沒意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍前往比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備守城嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心  這都是為了把信奈變成余的人的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止是朝倉軍  近衛和津田他們也逃進了比叡山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓他們逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.05,0:19:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍完全包圍了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣攻進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比叡山是有萬人信仰的總本山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果進攻的話  就等於和民眾為敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不值一提…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您三思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是與民眾為敵  我們至今到底是為了什麼而戰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子都死了啊  十兵衛也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們甘心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著怒氣用兵  0分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不為了天下萬民而戰  人民是不會跟著我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了  公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是難以攻入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要固守在這裡  信奈包圍網就能完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津田大人  其實啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就讓津田大人去做和睦的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和睦？我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.36,0:20:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去拖延時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有臉來見我啊  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是作為求和的使者來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛大人給我了書狀和禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  還來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重呢  到底送了什麼來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎？織田信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你的猴子連屍首都沒留下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你這個鄉下大名不識相才會變成這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是個安慰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著這個頭回國去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不悔改  還會白白犧牲很多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和家臣  還有雙親兄弟的人頭我會一個個砍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我什麼都不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走  去追公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出陣  公主大人出陣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下如你所願了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了信奈大人好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍前進  但不可以隨意進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相保持連攜進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了嗎…1分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不放過你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:35.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:40.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:55.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:01.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:12.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:23.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:33.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:43.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:35.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷時代紛爭的漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:40.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無奈佇立  獨自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:46.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在尋覓著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:50.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:55.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}堅韌的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:23:01.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住內心幽然淚下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:06.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿能聆聽到救贖之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:12.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有尋覓著的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:17.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經歷風花雪月的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:23.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:28.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再猶豫  願與你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:33.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之夢的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:43.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}請記住  屬於你的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:47.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
